videoDetails.Title: I Played 800 HOURS of War Thunder and got to TOP TIER
videoDetails.Description:
So the last video got age restricted, and had to be reuploaded, Deja Vu. I might have fixed it here, there's like a 50/50. So glad YouTube didn't tell me what the problem was when they "manually reviewed" it. Cheers.

After 4 Months, a lot of missing brain cells and countless hours it is finally finished. Hope you all enjoy :)
